test_792,2,4,"That's a good idea, thanks! Why do you take a boat to work? Does your city have canals?"
test_792,2,5,I have to take the ferry. It may be a little time consuming but it is so much fun to be out on the water everyday~
test_792,2,6,"I bet, I grew up by the ocean and I miss it very much. Do your kids visit you at the library?"
test_792,2,7,Oh it would be such a bummer to move away from it! Yes they do. Probably about once a week to pick up some more books! Do you enjoy working at the zoo?
