test_794,2,7,"Yeah, it can. But I love my patients. It nice to know all of the people they are like family."
test_794,2,8,That's cool. I'm sure it feels good to help people too. What kind of practice is it specifically?
test_794,2,9,Just a general practice so nothing special. 
test_794,2,10,Oh okay. Have you made any plans to go fishing soon?
test_794,2,11,"Yeah, I took a couple weeks off to go awhile for a little while. I just need a break from it all."
test_795,2,0,I just caught a huge fish! A tuna! Can you believe it? 
