test_795,2,2,"That might be a good idea! Yes it was super big, can't wait to figure out what I am going to do with it!"
test_795,2,3,That sounds fun! A fish fry or tuna salad. Do you make your tuna salad with eggs? What condiments do you put in it?
test_795,2,4,"No I don't use eggs, usually just mayo pickle relish, salt/pepper, and a little hot sauce."
