test_795,2,6,"No I don't think mustard is strange, I have actually tried it before and I thought it was good. I only caught the one tuna fish today."
test_795,2,7,It must've been pretty big sized!! Did anyone go with you to go fishing? I haven't went fishing in a while. I should make the day of it and drag the children with me. Haha. Any spots you recommend? 
