test_795,2,10,"She was just enjoying the sunshine. She can't stand fishing, does not have the patience haha."
test_795,2,11,I know I get frustrated when I sit there all day and don't catch anything. After a few hours I decide to swim. Or when a turtle snaps my line. That's very irritating.
