test_873,2,9,"Oh yes then that is definitely a stressful situation to be in. But, as long as you have your goals and you and your boss are working through with it I suppose."
test_873,2,10,So what is your work right now?
test_873,2,11,I'm an english tutor for 3-5th grade kids from South Korea!
test_876,2,0,What are small towns like?
test_876,2,1,"They're lonely, but a good lonely. I am glad to be away from the craziness of the city."
test_876,2,2,That's good! How many people live in yours?
test_876,2,3,About 250. It's strange whenever a newcomer visits the town because everybody knows everyone else here. How about your town?
test_876,2,4,"Right! It must be nice to have that sense of community with your neighbours? Where I live now is a bit larger, 2000 people or so"
test_876,2,5,"I can see how it would feel different having that many people near you. It still beats being crowded like you were in Britain though, huh?"
test_876,2,6,"Yes, everything is a bit more anonymous. Its nice to have a decent amount of land! What have you been up to this week?"
test_876,2,7,"Oh, I've been searching the stars the past couple nights. It's crazy to think about how big the universe is and how many stars there are. More than I could ever see anyway."
test_876,2,8,"How amazing! That's another thing about not living in a city, no light pollution! Do you have a telescope?"
test_876,2,9,Yep! I do have a telescope. It's old and cantankerous but it gets the job done. I'll let you use it some time.
test_876,2,10,"That would be great, thank you! What's the furthest star you can see with it?"
test_876,2,11,That would be Orion. I've watched that baby twinkle so many times.
test_878,2,0,Did I tell you the cool recipe I tried out today?
