test_885,2,7,"I don't attend church, but do have strong faith and try to live by example.  In a way, I see the world as one church."
test_885,2,8,That's a nice way to see the world. I often go to church with friends as my husband is away a lot. Do you have a lot of friends?
test_885,2,9,I have just a few close friends to share time with.  I prefer it that way.  I'm glad you have people to connect with through church.  
test_885,2,10,Better to have true friends rather than lots of friends I always say!
test_885,2,11,"That is an excellent perspective!  What kind of work does your husband do? My husband is in construction, but only travels a little."
test_886,2,0,"My daughters and I recently watched the new ""Conjuring"" movie. It was great!"
test_886,2,1,Really? I love horror movies I need to watch it. How is your other daughter doing?
test_886,2,2,"They're both doing fine.  They're busy at school and both doing well.  I'm so proud of them.  We rented the Conjuring as a reward because the older of the two got her first ""A"" on a History test."
test_886,2,3,"That's great! My kids are doing well in school too, they're both great kids!"
