test_900,2,6,"It's pretty easy, if it was just reading and tests it wouldn't be that much work. They add a lot of make-work (projects and class bulleting boards) though"
test_900,2,7,"That does sound like a lot, how much longer until you are a teacher?"
test_900,2,8,another semester of classes then a half year of pracitcum and I'm done
